text: Cedar Park is a major suburb of Austin in the state of Texas, the center of Austin is about to the southeast of Cedar Park. According to the U.S. Census, the city's population as of 2020 was 77,595. In 2017, Cedar Park adopted a new city flag, but abandoned it shortly after adoption following "pushback on social media" from residents. ==References== Category:Cities in Texas
title: Cedar Park, Texas
